org.eclipse.jst.jsf.facesconfig.edit.provider
Class FacesConfigItemProviderAdapterFactory

java.lang.Object
  AdapterFactoryImpl
      org.eclipse.jst.jsf.facesconfig.emf.util.FacesConfigAdapterFactory
          org.eclipse.jst.jsf.facesconfig.edit.provider.FacesConfigItemProviderAdapterFactory

public class FacesConfigItemProviderAdapterFactory
extends FacesConfigAdapterFactory

This is the factory that is used to provide the interfaces needed to support Viewers. The adapters generated by this factory convert EMF adapter notifications into calls to fireNotifyChanged. The adapters also support Eclipse property sheets. Note that most of the adapters are shared among multiple instances.
